headline: Is Uber a No-Brainer Growth Stock to Buy in 2025?
summary: Uber (NYSE: UBER) has become so successful since its founding in 2009 that its name is used interchangeably as a verb when taking a ride somewhere.  This demonstrates the incredible mindshare it has developed with consumers, thanks to the company's ability to create an entirely new category within the transportation sector.  At the time of this writing, shares of Uber trade 20% off their peak, but they have soared 134% in the past 24 months, crushing the overall market.
